comments: Allen (CLE) sets the screen in Schroder's (LAL) path and does not deliver contact.
Allen (CLE) sets the screen on Caruso (LAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Caruso (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position on Sexton (CLE) and absorbs the contact as Sexton loses control of the ball.
Schroder (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position on Sexton (CLE) following the pick.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) makes contact with Osman's (CLE) arm and affects his ability to pass.
Osman (CLE) reaches in and makes contact with Davis's (LAL) head.
Prince (CLE) makes marginal contact with Schroder (LAL) during the drive.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) makes marginal contact with Osman (CLE) before he begins his upward shooting motion.
